    <section>
      <h1><img src='img/bitcoin/integration.svg' alt>Simple integration</h1>
      <p>Two options: an easy <a href='docs/guides/bitcoin'>API</a> for your own form, or enable in
      <a href='country?country=CH&amp;redirect=%252Fcheckout'>Checkout</a> with just a few lines.</p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h1><img src='img/bitcoin/predictable.svg' alt>Fluctuation-resistant</h1>
      <p>Avoid exchange rate hassles—specify amounts in USD and we’ll send you dollars.</p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h1><img src='img/bitcoin/pricing.svg' alt>Transparent pricing</h1>
      <p>Stripe charges just 0.8% per successful Bitcoin transaction, capped at $5. There are no other fees.</p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h1><img src='img/bitcoin/reports.svg' alt>Unified reports</h1>
      <p>No extra hassle: Bitcoin payments are integrated into the <a href='https://dashboard.stripe.com'>same reporting</a> as credit cards.</p>
    </section>
